<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idef75bcd0-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s2208a"><num value="2208a">§ 2208a.</num><heading> Loan levels provided to Department of Agriculture</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">On and after <date date="2005-11-10">November 10, 2005</date>, loan levels provided in this or any other Appropriations Act to the Department of Agriculture shall be considered estimates, not limitations.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idef75bcd1-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/pl/109/97/tVII/s710">Pub. L. 109–97, title VII, § 710</ref>, <date date="2005-11-10">Nov. 10, 2005</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/119/2150">119 Stat. 2150</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
